    {
      "id": "agent-details",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 985,
      "y": 200,
      "width": 335,
      "height": 280,
      "text": "ProcessManager\n  Bounded concurrency pool (20 max)\n  Queue overflow jobs\n\nrunAgent()\n  Claude SDK agentic loop (5min timeout)\n  Gemini support via isGeminiModel()\n\nStreamFlusher\n  Debounced DB updates (50-100ms)\n\nbuildMcpServer() — dynamic tools\nbuildSystemPrompt() — context builder\n\nEndpoints:\n  POST  /dispatch/job\n  POST  /api/:agentId/:slug\n  GET   /health\n\nAuth: AGENT_SERVER_TOKEN",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 303,
