      "roundness": null,
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "ProcessManager\n  Bounded concurrency pool (20 max)\n  Queue overflow jobs\n\nrunAgent()\n  Claude SDK agentic loop (5min timeout)\n  Gemini support via isGeminiModel()\n\nStreamFlusher\n  Debounced DB updates (50-100ms)\n\nbuildMcpServer() — dynamic tools\nbuildSystemPrompt() — context builder\n\nEndpoints:\n  POST  /dispatch/job\n  POST  /api/:agentId/:slug\n  GET   /health\n\nAuth: AGENT_SERVER_TOKEN",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },

